## Execution Rules

1. **Stay focused** - Only implement what's described in this subtask
2. **Be self-contained** - Your changes should not depend on other in-progress subtasks
3. **Follow patterns** - Use existing code patterns from the codebase
4. **Document changes** - Add appropriate comments and documentation
5. **Validate locally** - Run relevant tests before completing

## Completion Criteria

Mark your subtask complete when:
- [ ] All described functionality is implemented
- [ ] Code follows project conventions
- [ ] Relevant tests pass
- [ ] No linter errors introduced

## Output

When complete, provide a summary of:
1. Files modified/created
2. Key implementation decisions
3. Any edge cases handled
4. Tests added or verified
